title: 51A.50 FEDERAL ASSOCIATIONS.
text: The following sections apply to federal associations, except to the extent they are inconsistent with federal law or regulations: sections 47.59; 51A.01; 51A.02; 51A.065; 51A.15, subdivision 6; 51A.21, subdivisions 6a, 15, 16, 22, 25, 27, and 28; 51A.23, subdivision 1; 51A.24; 51A.251; 51A.261; 51A.262; 51A.27; 51A.28; 51A.29; 51A.30; 51A.31; 51A.37, subdivisions 1, 2, 3, paragraphs (a), (c), (d), 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, and 12; 51A.38; 51A.386; 51A.40; 51A.50; 51A.52; 51A.56; and 51A.57.
